{
  "id": null,
  "title": "Enterprise SRE Dashboard - Error Budgets, SLOs & Reliability Engineering",
  "tags": ["sre", "error-budget", "slo", "reliability", "enterprise"],
  "style": "dark",
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-7d",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "üéØ SLO Compliance (28-day rolling window)",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "((sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\",status_code!~\"5..\"}[28d])) or vector(0)) / (sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\"}[28d])) or vector(1))) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Backend SLO: 99.95%",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "((sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\",status!~\"5..\"}[28d])) or vector(0)) / (sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\"}[28d])) or vector(1))) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service SLO: 99.5%",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "avg_over_time(probe_success{instance=\"https://todo-app.natsuki-cloud.dev\"}[28d]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Frontend SLO: 99.9%",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 99,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": 99},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 99.5},
              {"color": "green", "value": 99.9}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0}
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "üí∞ Error Budget Remaining (Monthly)",
      "type": "gauge",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"backend-service\"} * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Backend (Target: 99.95%)",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"ai-service\"} * 100",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service (Target: 99.5%)",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "probe_success * 100",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": 0},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 25},
              {"color": "green", "value": 75}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6}
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "üìä System Health Overview",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"backend-service\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Backend",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"ai-service\"}", 
          "legendFormat": "AI Service",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "probe_success",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}",
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "Backend {{status_code}}",
          "refId": "D"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service {{status}}", 
          "refId": "E"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {"options": {"0": {"text": "‚ùå DOWN"}}, "type": "value"},
            {"options": {"1": {"text": "‚úÖ UP"}}, "type": "value"}
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": 0},
              {"color": "green", "value": 1}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byRegex", "options": "/.*Traffic.*/"}, 
            "properties": [
              {"id": "unit", "value": "reqps"},
              {"id": "mappings", "value": []},
              {"id": "thresholds", "value": {
                "steps": [
                  {"color": "red", "value": 0},
                  {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.01},
                  {"color": "green", "value": 0.1}
                ]
              }}
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6}
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "üìä SLO Performance Trend (7 days)",
      "type": "timeseries", 
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "((sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\",status_code!~\"5..\"}[1h])) or vector(0)) / (sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\"}[1h])) or vector(1))) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Backend Availability %",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "((sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\",status!~\"5..\"}[1h])) or vector(0)) / (sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\"}[1h])) or vector(1))) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service Availability %",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "probe_success{instance=\"https://todo-app.natsuki-cloud.dev\"} * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Frontend Availability %",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 99,
          "max": 100,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 14}
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "üö® Current Alerts Status",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{alertname}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "count(ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Total Firing Alerts",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": [
            {"options": {"0": {"text": "‚úÖ All Systems Normal"}}, "type": "value"}
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": 0},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
              {"color": "red", "value": 3}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 14}
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "‚ö° Latency SLO Compliance",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"backend-service\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Backend p95 (SLO: <200ms)",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"ai-service\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service p95 (SLO: <2s)",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "probe_duration_seconds{instance=\"https://todo-app.natsuki-cloud.dev\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Frontend Load Time (SLO: <2s)",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": 0},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.2},
              {"color": "red", "value": 2}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 22}
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "üìà Traffic Patterns & Capacity",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Backend Total Traffic",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service Total Traffic",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{pod=~\"todo-.*\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Total CPU Usage",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Total CPU Usage"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "unit", "value": "short"}
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 22}
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "üìã SRE Metrics Summary",
      "type": "table",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "probe_success{job=\"blackbox-external-targets\"}",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "__name__": true,
              "Time": true,
              "job": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "instance": "Service Endpoint",
              "Value": "Availability Status"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "displayMode": "table"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {"options": {"0": {"text": "‚ùå DOWN", "color": "red"}}, "type": "value"},
            {"options": {"1": {"text": "‚úÖ UP", "color": "green"}}, "type": "value"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 30}
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "üéØ SLO Targets & Business Impact",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 30},
      "options": {
        "content": "## üìä SLO Definitions & Error Budgets\n\n### üéØ Service Level Objectives:\n- **Backend API**: 99.95% availability, <200ms p95 latency\n- **AI Service**: 99.5% availability, <2s p95 latency  \n- **Frontend**: 99.9% availability, <2s page load\n\n### üí∞ Monthly Error Budgets:\n- **Backend**: 21.6 minutes downtime allowed\n- **AI Service**: 3.6 hours downtime allowed\n- **Frontend**: 43.2 minutes downtime allowed\n\n### üî• Burn Rate Alerts:\n- **Critical**: >14.4x rate (2h to exhaust budget)\n- **High**: >6x rate (5h to exhaust budget)\n- **Medium**: >2x rate (15h to exhaust budget)\n\n### üìà Key Business Metrics:\n- **MTTR**: Mean Time To Recovery\n- **MTBF**: Mean Time Between Failures\n- **Change Success Rate**: Deployment reliability\n- **Alert Quality**: Signal vs noise ratio"
      }
    }
  ]
}